      • onStarted

        @Deprecated
public void onStarted(WifiConfiguration wifiConfiguration)
        已过时。 This callback is deprecated. Use #onStarted(SoftApConfiguration)) instead.
        Called when access point started successfully.

        Note that AP detail may contain configuration which is cannot be represented by the legacy WifiConfiguration, in such cases a null will be returned. For example:

      • SoftAp band in WifiConfiguration.apBand only supports 2GHz, 5GHz, 2GHz+5GHz bands, so conversion is limited to these bands.
      • SoftAp security type in WifiConfiguration.KeyMgmt only supports NONE, WPA2_PSK, so conversion is limited to these security type.
参数:
wifiConfiguration - the WifiConfiguration of the current hotspot.

  • onStarted

    public void onStarted(SoftApConfiguration softApConfiguration)
    Called when access point started successfully.
    参数:

  • onStopped

    public void onStopped()

  • onFailed

    public void onFailed(int reason)
    Called when access point failed to start. No events will be sent after that.
